{"tid":328693,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"夜晚聽歌真係好撚正","createTime":"2017-07-19T18:34:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T00:39:53.000Z","uid":91482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"624b5c25bfbc5625183402b505c99f4abb5c1990","tid":328693,"uid":91482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T18:34:50.000Z","msg":"音樂係夜晚最好既心靈雞湯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一條友熄曬燈塞住對耳聽歌 <br />\n真係好爽。<br />\n環境越靜越好 會有種離世感<br />\n仔細聽歌詞 每句都會打到入心入肺<br />\n寂寞又絕望 特別有feel 好享受  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n尤其係聽張敬軒同鄭中基啲歌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽聽下諗起回憶 就眼泛淚光 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不妨分享下啲歌或者歌詞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-cDq9maci4w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-cDq9maci4w&d=K7RWQkCtLu4qg1hphS3gAmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=5590396d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-cDq9maci4w</a>"},{"pid":"edda688ff9994425d3bfa10d0d23b4dada52c8ce","tid":328693,"uid":25323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T18:35:37.000Z","msg":"張敬軒 - 襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a16a85648c59f4dd113cc4c4cd5f35161edf8cfe","tid":328693,"uid":89182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T18:36:16.000Z","msg":"With whiskey 🥃<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a6a124159c350cb85fc0cbb44824e2b04b2d5a","tid":328693,"uid":55664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T18:36:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nKQsYyd1pZ0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.l